{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"DOMRect","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect/fromRect\"><code>fromRect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Geometry Interfaces</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrix\"><code>DOMMatrix</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrixReadOnly\"><code>DOMMatrixReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>一个&nbsp;<strong><code>DOMRect</code></strong>&nbsp;代表一个矩形。</p>\n\n<p><code>DOMRect</code>&nbsp;表示的盒子的类型由返回它的方法或属性指定。例如，WebVR API 的 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters\"><code>VREyeParameters.renderRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 指定了头戴式显示器的一只眼睛应该呈现的影像所在的&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\">canvas</a>&nbsp;的视口。</p>\n\n<p>它继承自它的父类，<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly</code></a>。</p>\n\n<p><svg viewBox=\"-1 -1 650 42\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin meet\">\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly\">\n    <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"120\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"60\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      DOMRectReadOnly\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"120\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"150\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" \"=\"\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"120,14 130,9 130,19 120,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\" aria-current=\"page\">\n    <rect x=\"150\" y=\"0\" width=\"75\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#F4F7F8\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"187.5\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      DOMRect\n    </text>\n  </a></svg></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"构造函数","title":"构造函数","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"domrect\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect/DOMRect\" title=\"DOMRect()\"><code>DOMRect()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>创建一个新的&nbsp;<code>DOMRect</code> 对象。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n</dl>\n\n<p><code>DOMRect</code>&nbsp;从其父类&nbsp;<em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly</code></a></em> 继承属性。不同之处在于它们不再是只读的。</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.x_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/x\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.x</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>DOMRect</code>&nbsp;原点的 x 坐标。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.y_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/y\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.y</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>DOMRect</code>&nbsp;原点的 y&nbsp;坐标。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.width_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/width\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.width</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>DOMRect</code> 的宽度。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.height_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/height\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.height</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>DOMRect</code>&nbsp;的高度。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.top_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/top\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.top</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>返回 <code>DOMRect</code> 的顶坐标值（与 <code>y</code> 具有相同的值，如果 <code>height</code> 为负值，则为&nbsp;<code>y + height</code>&nbsp;的值）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.right_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/right\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.right</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>返回 <code>DOMRect</code> 的右坐标值（与 <code>x + width</code> 具有相同的值，如果<code>width</code> 为负值，则为&nbsp;<code>x</code> 的值）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.bottom_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/bottom\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.bottom</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>返回 <code>DOMRect</code> 的底坐标值（与 <code>y + height</code> 具有相同的值，如果 <code>height</code> 为负值，则为 <code>y</code>&nbsp;的值）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.left_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/left\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.left</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>返回 <code>DOMRect</code> 的左坐标值（与 <code>x</code> 具有相同的值，如果 <code>width</code>&nbsp;为负值，则为&nbsp;<code>x + width</code>&nbsp;的值）。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em><code>DOMRect</code> 从它的父类继承方法，<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly</code></a>。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect1\">\n <h2 id=\"静态方法\">静态方法</h2>\n </dt>\n <dt id=\"domrectreadonly.fromrect_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly/fromRect\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly.fromRect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>创建一个具有指定位置和尺寸的新 <code>DOMRect</code> 对象。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"specification","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.fxtf.org/geometry/#DOMRect","title":"Geometry Interfaces Module Level 1"}],"query":"api.DOMRect"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.DOMRect","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"更多","title":"更多","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"构造函数","id":"构造函数"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"规范","id":"specification"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"更多","id":"更多"}],"summary":"一个 DOMRect 代表一个矩形。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DOMRect","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DOMRect","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"DOMRect","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"DOMRect","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/domrect","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/domrect/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect","title":"DOMRect"}],"pageTitle":"DOMRect - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}